 1.e4 c5 2.Nf3 d6 3.d4 cxd4 4.Nxd4 Nf6 5.Nc3 a6 6.Rg1 { White wants to play g4-g5 } ( 6.Bd3 ) { although i suggest first 6...e5 7.Nb3 and only now 7... h5 , I decided to include this game..because it has many typical ideas and mistakes of the Najdorf! } 6...h5 ( 6...b5 7.g4 Bb7 8.Bg2 Nfd7 9.Be3 g6 ) ( 6...e5 { is the best move. } 7.Nb3 h5 8.h3 h4 ) ( 6...e6 $6 7.g4 Be7 8.g5 Nfd7 9.Be3 b5 10.a3 Bb7 11.Qd2 Nc6 12.O-O-O O-O 13.Nxc6 Bxc6 14.f4 { Such positions are very dangerous for Black. } ) 7.h3 ( 7.Bg5 $5 Nbd7 8.Qd2 ) 7...g6 8.Be3 e5 { is not a good move now because of 9.Nf3 and planning Ng5 } 9.Nb3 ( 9.Nf3 { is better } 9...Qc7 ( 9...Be7 10.Bc4 Be6 11.Bb3 ) 10.Ng5 ) 9...Be6 10.Qe2 $6 ( 10.g4 hxg4 11.hxg4 Nbd7 12.g5 ( 12.Qe2 Rc8 13.g5 ( 13.O-O-O Rxc3 ) 13...Rxc3 14.bxc3 Nxe4 ) 12...Nh5 13.Qd2 Rc8 14.O-O-O Be7 15.Rh1 ( 15.Be2 ) 15...Nb6 16.Kb1 Nc4 17.Bxc4 Rxc4 18.f3 ) 10...Nbd7 { Intending Rc8 and sacrifice on c3. } 11.O-O-O ( 11.g4 hxg4 12.hxg4 Rc8 13.g5 Rxc3 ) 11...Rc8 12.f4 ( 12.Qd2 b5 13.f3 Nb6 $1 ( 13...h4 $1 $132 ) 14.Bd3 $2 ( 14.Kb1 $1 Nc4 ( 14...b4 15.Qf2 ( 15.Ne2 $2 Nc4 16.Qc1 a5 $19 ) ) 15.Bxc4 bxc4 16.Nc1 ) 14...Nc4 15.Bxc4 bxc4 16.Na1 Rb8 $17 17.Bg5 Qb6 ) ( 12.Bd2 b5 ( 12...h4 ) ( 12...Be7 ) 13.a3 Nb6 ( 13...h4 ) ( 13...Bxb3 14.cxb3 Nc5 15.Kb1 Nxb3 16.Bg5 Nd4 17.Qd3 Be7 ) ( 13...Be7 ) ) ( 12.Nd5 Nxe4 ( 12...Nxd5 13.exd5 Bf5 14.c3 Nb6 ( 14...h4 ) ) ( 12...Bxd5 13.exd5 Bg7 14.g4 O-O ) ) ( 12.f3 Rxc3 ) 12...Rxc3 13.bxc3 Nxe4 { Black is already winning. } 14.Bd4 $2 Ng3 { not the best move. } ( 14...f5 $3 { - 4.50 !!! } 15.fxe5 dxe5 16.Bxe5 Qg5+ { Unfortunately, I failed to find this move. } ) 15.Qf3 Nxf1 16.fxe5 Qg5+ 17.Kb2 dxe5 18.Bf2 Qf5 19.Qxb7 Qxf2 20.Rgxf1 Qe2 21.Rfe1 Qb5 22.Qc8+ Ke7 23.Qc7 Bg7 ( 23...Bh6 24.c4 Qb8 25.Rxd7+ Bxd7 26.Rxe5+ Kf6 27.Qxd7 Qxe5+ ) 24.Qd6+ Ke8 25.Qc7 Bf6 26.a4 Qxa4 27.Rd2 Kf8 28.Ra1 Qb5 29.Ra5 Qf1 30.Qa7 Kg7 31.Rxa6 ( 31.Rxd7 Bxd7 32.Qxd7 e4 ) 31...Qc4 ( 31...Bf5 32.Rxd7 Bxd7 33.Qxd7 Qxa6 ) 32.Rxe6 Qxe6 33.Rxd7 Rd8 34.Nc5 Qc4 35.Qb6 Rc8 36.Ne6+ Kh6 37.Nc7 Bg5 38.Nd5 Qf1 39.Ne3 Qf4 40.Qb7 Rf8 41.Nd5 Qc1+ 42.Kb3 Rb8 

